# ── Recipe image uploads (T04) ──
# Files land in public/recipes/ at runtime via the image-upload flow. Keep the
# directory tracked (so the storage path always exists after clone) but never
# commit user-uploaded images.
public/recipes/*
!public/recipes/.gitkeep
